tafsir[4]{c,v,t}:
  112,1,"Maaku-aan nelaaɗo- ko Kanko woni gooto e Alliyankaagal, alah dewatee e goongo si wona Kanko."
  112,2,"Ko kanko woni koohoowo mbo koongu haaɗti nder sifaaji timmal e njooɗndam, Mbo tagaaɓe paandato."
  112,3,"Oon mbo jibinaani O jibinaaka,O jibinaani hay gooto,O alah ɓiɓɗɗo-Kanko ceniiɗo O- O alah jiknaaɗo."
  112,4,"Woodanaani Mbo pasa hay gooto."
